description:
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a full time Band 6 Clinical Specialist role for a highly motivated Dermatology position.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Dermatology service at University Hospital Coventry &amp; Warwickshire provides a service at UHCW, GEH and rugby sites with scope for looking at developing the service further.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are currently reviewing the Dermatology service and will look to cross cover within the Dermatology footprint in the community.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This post will look to facilitate an innovative review of the whole service. We are looking for a friendly, enthusiastic and forward thinking individual to lead, develop and improve patient experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You must have a proven track record of demonstrating diabetes knowledge and skills, an effective role model and self-motivated individual with drive and adaptability to cope with continuously changing services.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will need to work closely with the Modern Matron for Specialist Medicine and other healthcare professions within University Hospital Coventry and Warwickshire and Coventry CWPT and CCG.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameSimon GorrellJob titleModern MatronEmail addresssimon.gorrell@uhcw.nhs.ukTelephone number02476964000 ask for bleep 5546Additional contact information&lt;/p&gt;
